c: 4
v: 57
t: "Asi avo vanotenda (muhumwechete hwaAllah) uye vachiita mabasa akanaka, tichava tinovaisa mumapindu umo muine nzizi dzinoerera pasi pawo, umo vachagara nekusingaperi. Varimo, vachawana vakadzi vakachenurwa (nevarume vakachenurwa), uye tichavaisa mumvuri hombe usingaperi (unotonhorera)"